Hey all. When working in git lets conform to some best practices.

1. The first rule of group work on git is NEVER PUSH TO MAIN. <http://NEVER.EVER.PUSH.TO|NEVER.EVER.PUSH.TO>.MAIN.  :slightly_smiling_face: LOL
2. Make a branch. something like  feature-`your name` - `name of feature`
3. When itâ€™s time to merge into main I will help the first time or two, until we are comfortable doing that process with other team members.
Happy coding!
